        <text>
         <body>
      <lg>
        <l>Goaded and harassed in the factory</l> 
      </lg>
      <lg rend ="indent1">
        <l>That tears our life up into bits of days</l>
        <l>Ticked off upon a clock which never stays,</l>
      </lg>
      <lg>
        <l>Shredding our portion of Eternity,</l>
        <l>We break away at last, and steal the key</l>
      </lg>
      <lg rend ="indent1">
        <l>Which hides a world empty of hours; ways</l>
        <l>Of space unroll, and Heaven overlays</l>
      </lg>
      <lg>
        <l>The leafy, sun-lit earth of Fantasy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg rend ="indent1">
        <l>Beyond the ilex shadow glares the sun,</l>
        <l>Scorching against the blue flame of the sky.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg>
        <l>Brown lily-pads lie heavy and supine</l>
      </lg>
      <lg rend ="indent1">
        <l>Within a granite basin, under one</l>
        <l>The bronze-gold glimmer of a carp; and I</l>
      </lg>
      <lg>
        <l>Reach out my hand and pluck a nectarine.</l>
      </lg>
